END QUOTE<br>
<br>
I once saw a guy pull a rabbit out of a hat... I must be an expert at slight of hand then!  From your example I only need to SEE it to become a master!<br>
Sorry, experience is the only teacher in both cases.  I have it when it comes to shadowknights... you don't (obviously).<br>
