Take a look at all of the Class-only armor sets in every expansion.  Crafted/Darkforge, Cobalt/BE, Plane of Growth, Dorf/Giant/Dragon quest armors, Twilight armors, Ornate armors, Elemental Armors.....  the warrior versions have more Hp and AC in nearly every case.  Unless you are on the &quot;uber&quot; side of the scale and wearing VT gear, the warriors will have more AC/HP (and now ATK and regen as well) from their equipment than Knights do.<br>
<br>
QUOTE<br>
