-Damage bonuses being scaled correctly for ALL weapons.. this includes high delay 1H weapons, and low delay 2H....<br>
-More itemization variations overall...  why is it always everyone gets &quot;X&quot; sword for 2H and &quot;Y&quot; and &quot;Z&quot; for dual wield because everything else is so bad in comparison?<br>
